      "id": "overview",
      "title": "Role Overview",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": {
            "text": "Engineering Manager interviews assess your ability to lead teams, deliver results, grow engineers, and maintain technical credibility. Expect a mix of leadership scenarios, technical discussions, and system design."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": {
            "text": "**What interviewers assess:**\n\n- People management and team building\n- Technical judgment and architecture skills\n- Delivery and execution track record\n- Handling conflict and difficult situations\n- Hiring, coaching, and growing engineers"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "format",
      "title": "Common Interview Format",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": {
            "text": "**Typical EM interview loop:**\n\n1. **Recruiter screen** (30 min)\n2. **Hiring manager screen** (60 min) - Leadership philosophy, background\n3. **Onsite/Virtual loop** (5-6 hours):\n   - Leadership/people management round\n   - Technical/system design round\n   - Cross-functional collaboration round\n   - Execution/delivery round\n   - Bar raiser/culture fit round"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "tip",
          "content": {
            "text": "Have specific examples ready for: firing someone, handling underperformers, resolving team conflict, and making difficult prioritization calls."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
